### Android Map Directory API — quick tests
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension. Edit @baseUrl / @apiKey as needed.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiKey = change-me-to-a-long-random-secret

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories

### All places
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/places

### Filter by category (slug)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/places?category=cafe

### Search by keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/places?q=kopi

### Sort by distance from a point
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/places?lat=-7.2756&lng=112.7946&sort=distance&limit=10

### Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/places?limit=5&offset=5

### Place detail (with distance)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/places/1?lat=-7.2756&lng=112.7946

### Create place (admin) — requires X-API-Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/places
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "category_id": 1,
  "name": "Kafe Baru",
  "latitude": -7.2760,
  "longitude": 112.7950,
  "address": "Jl. Kampus No. 99",
  "opening_hours": "08:00-22:00",
  "description": "Kafe baru dekat gerbang.",
  "rating": 4.3,
  "photo_url": "https://picsum.photos/seed/new/400/300"
}

### Update place (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/places/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "rating": 4.9,
  "description": "Deskripsi diperbarui."
}

### Unauthorized write (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/places
Content-Type: application/json

{ "category_id": 1, "name": "Tanpa Key", "latitude": -7.27, "longitude": 112.79 }

### Add review
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/places/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Tempatnya nyaman!",
  "user_id": "device-123"
}
